description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THIS POST IS FIXED TERM/SECONDMENT FOR 18 MONTHS TO MEET THE NEEDS OF THE SERVICE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IF YOU ARE INTERESTED IN APPLYING FOR THE SECONDMENT POSITION, YOU MUST OBTAIN PERMISSION FROM YOUR CURRENT LINE MANAGER PRIOR TO APPLYING FOR THIS POST&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Project Officer to join our Single Record team on a 18 month contract. Working as part of the programme, the post holder will be responsible for supporting the national Welsh Information System for Diabetes Management (WISDM) project in addition to other key Single Record priority projects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit a highly organised and motivated individual. Working in a challenging environment, you will face a variety of competing priorities that will require a flexible and imaginative approach combined with excellent interpersonal, communication and organisation skills. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The post requires experience of administering projects and knowledge of techniques for planning, monitoring and controlling projects.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Good computer skills, including Microsoft Office Suite, are necessary together with the ability to master new applications. Attention to detail and accuracy are essential skills for this post. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You will ideally have previous NHS and/or IM&amp;T project experience, together with knowledge of PRINCE II.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Above all, we will be looking for the results driven approach, and the motivation necessary to meet the service needs of the organisation.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like to discuss this post further, please contact Laurence James, Single Record Programme Manager.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date: 19th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Laurence James - Programme Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Laurence.James@wales.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
